      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_4257810988028056564.png",
                "id": "talent38791",
                "key": "直率的辞绝",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "直率的辞绝"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">岩元素附魔</span>；从手牌中<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">舍弃</span>至多5张<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">裂晶弹片</span>，每<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">舍弃</span>1张都使此伤害+1并抓1张牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/d13eff9275ac9df191b4e1f83bdd18c7_3068132437060674191.png",
                "id": "talent22582",
                "key": "典仪式晶火",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "典仪式晶火"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素伤害</span>，对所有敌方后台角色造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透伤害</span>。召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">金花礼炮</span>，生成1张<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">裂晶弹片</span>加入手牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/25547c6b405dc204653b701c121b1096_4669300196432240680.png",
                "id": "talent48172",
                "key": "如霰澄天的鸣礼",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "如霰澄天的鸣礼"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">敌方角色受到结晶反应伤害后：</span>生成3张<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">裂晶弹片</span>，随机置入我方牌库中。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/7e023ac7d7c52126ccbea78e74621bfd_8444543279154100948.png",
                "id": "talent91943",
                "key": "互助关系网",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "互助关系网"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素伤害</span>，抓1张<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">裂晶弹片</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7717691358285154230.png",
                "id": "talent57499",
                "key": "金花礼炮",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/ca5315848113a22db13d032f358ddbdb_3365543621380359422.png",
                "title": "金花礼炮"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">事件牌</span></p><p>对敌方「出战角色」造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>，抓1张牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/20/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7283120486034626153.png",
                "key": "裂晶弹片",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "white"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/20/157749474/ca5315848113a22db13d032f358ddbdb_772994211052370611.png",
                "title": "裂晶弹片"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">结晶（冰）</span>：本伤害<span>+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">结晶（水）</span>：本伤害<span>+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">结晶（火）</span>：本伤害<span>+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">结晶（雷）</span>：本伤害<span>+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_7187526615368512462.png",
                "id": "talent79438",
                "key": "岩元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">岩元素附魔</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p>所附属角色造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>，变为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span></strong></p><p>通过行动牌或角色技能的效果，将行动牌从手牌或牌库中弃置。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合结束阶段，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_9019805748613925958.png",
